{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/Header.png?t=1733979187\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome, comrade Commander!</h2><strong>Multi Turret Academy</strong> is a top-down tank action game with roguelike elements. Select your vehicle from a growing list of historical models, then equip dozens of weapons and upgrades to lead your local tank club to victory!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/Battle.gif?t=1733979187\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Choice is Yours</h2>A growing selection of WWII tanks awaits, as you decide how to achieve victory on the field of battle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/ChangeTank_EN.gif?t=1733979187\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Modify Tank</h2>During playthrough, you can freely dismantle turrets from your tank and replace it with the turrets from other vehicles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/ChangeTurret_EN.gif?t=1733979187\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Recruit Crews</h2>Each student in  the tank club has unique talents. Recruiting them into your crew during battles will grant your vehicle new abilities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/11EN.png?t=1733979187\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733979187","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733979187","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/f0afb27e8435746f4c3232f7789c24267b69056e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733979187","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat